    <article class="article">
      <header class="article-header">
        <h1 title="該如何將小說預設為豎版表示？" class="article-title">
          該如何將小說預設為豎版表示？
          
        </h1>

        
      </header>

      <section class="article-info">
        <div class="article-content">
          <div class="article-body"><p>可於小說投稿畫面將作品預設為豎版表示。</p>
<p>▶<a href="#h_01FM3Z10AYQQ0T8F7XP7TCJJNZ" target="_self">電腦版</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM3Z17ZRV56PPV3A91E4KCEX" target="_self">手機版</a><br>▶<a href="#h_01FM3Z1EVGT1MVSVHD4JFVT5T6" target="_self">應用程式版</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM3Z10AYQQ0T8F7XP7TCJJNZ">電腦版</h3>
<p>於投稿畫面中展開詳細設置。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409248931737/02_____________.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409248931737/02_____________.png" alt="02_____________.png" width="518" height="520"></a></p>
<p>開啟「外觀效果」選項中的「默認為豎版表示」即可。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409242582425/02_____________02.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409242582425/02_____________02.png" alt="02_____________02.png" width="529" height="510"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM3Z17ZRV56PPV3A91E4KCEX">手機版</h3>
<p>於投稿畫面中展開其他設定後，開啟「默認為豎版表示」即可。</p>
<p><a href="/hc/article_attachments/4409235211417/02___________01.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img src="/hc/article_attachments/4409235211417/02___________01.png" alt="02___________01.png" width="493" height="924"></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3 id="h_01FM3Z1EVGT1MVSVHD4JFVT5T6">應用程式版</h3>
<p>目前應用程式版尚未支援豎版表示。</p></div>

          <div class="article-attachments">
            <ul class="attachments">
              
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

